headline: Republic Services and Teamsters reach 5-year agreement in Boston
summary: The new collective bargaining agreement brings a monthslong strike to an end. The strike, which kicked off July 1, triggered a wave of labor action from other Teamsters this summer that at one point included 2,000 workers.
